Flashcards Page:
As a user, I can see 1 flashcard at a time that shows an array prototype method
In order to view the answer/definition, I can click on the see answer button on each card. 
By clicking on the link at the bottom, I can see more information and examples of each method.
 
If I want to scroll to the next flashcard or back to the previous flashcard, I can click on arrows to the right or left of the flash card. 
To exit the individual flashcard, I can click an X by the flashcard. 
